metadata.name: REFLECTIONS NOIR #1
metadata.description: Reflections Noir is the follow-up to the hugely successful debut collection by Rich Simmons. After every gallery show, the artist creates a monochromatic version of his favourite piece for his own collection.Reflections Noir continues this tradition by creating a monochromatic series that celebrates more artists that inspires Simmons work and career.By offering this exclusively to holders of the original Reflections NFT series, Simmons shows his commitment to building a solid community and offering continued utility, excitement, quality, and inspiration through his collections.Your collection description
